OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNew probation boss: 'We    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fneed more men'             
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The new head of the probation service  
OL,6, in England and Wales has told BBC News 
OL,7, that more men are needed in the        
OL,8, profession.                            
OL,10,FKim Thornden-Edwards said it would help
OL,11,Fto bring a male perspective in some    
OL,12,Fcases involving violent offenders,     
OL,13,Fincluding cases of domestic abuse.     
OL,15,FIts workforce has been "stuck" at 75%  
OL,16,Fwomen for 30 years, she added.         
OL,18,FShe also said older people with life   
OL,19,Fexperiences are needed, including those
OL,20,Fwho have been on probation themselves. 
